==English==
===Etymology===
From the Latin [[granum|granulum]], little grain.
===Noun===
'''granule'''
# A tiny [[grain]], a small [[particle]].
#{{geology}} a [[fragment]] of [[rock]] etc., [[larger]] than a [[sand]] [[grain]] and [[smaller]] than a [[pebble]]
#{{astronomy}} a small [[mark]] in the [[photosphere]] of the [[sun]] caused by [[convection]] [[current]]s

